article_title: Trump: ObamaCare Not Working For Business, Going to Collapse
article_text:
SIGN UP FOR OUR NEWSLETTER





This week on Fox News Radio’s “Vipp Jaswal Report,” real estate mogul Donald Trump said the biggest current hindrance to America business is ObamaCare which he predicted will “fall on it’s own weight.”

“ObamaCare has to be ended,” Trump said. “The cost is so high and you know people who had good plans don’t have good plans anymore. They don’t have their doctors anymore, and the deductibles are so high. I think its going to fall on it’s own weight.”
